The body of a young girl (Laura Palmer) is washed up on a beach near the small 
Washington state town of Twin Peaks. FBI Special Agent Dale Cooper is called 
in to investigate her strange demise, only to uncover a web of mystery that
ultimately leads him deep into the heart of the surrounding woodland, and his 
very own soul.
